column5: heading up to lake eugenia, coming from the southwest. ive never been there before and am not sure where the launch is im sure there is more than one but can someone give me a road to come in on,,thanks

Go to Flesherton, take Grey Rd 4 east to Grey Rd 13 north, keep an eye right for Canrobert St, turn right, down the road, park and launch on the left, be prepared to pay, $10 the last time I was there a few years ago.  Check google maps, you'll see the open white spot, it's the parking lot.  The straight line above it is the dam.
Only one launch and its $17 now.
